---
title: Creamy Chicken Korma Baked Naan with chilli butter potatoes and tomato salsa
description: Golden baked naans are topped with a rich, creamy and slightly sweet chicken korma in this indulgent dish. Cut through the richness with a side of chilli potatoes and a refreshing tomato salsa!
